Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.40,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，卡萊多之星就要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星的時候請保持室內的亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家擅長的本領是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烹飪？運動？學習？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.10,0:00:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞呢，十分擅長創作與編寫故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會寫出什麼樣的故事呢？真讓人興奮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.80,0:00:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊！美亞！讓我們一起來期待吧！吧！吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周之內必須讓這個劇本能夠上演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之三天之內交出劇本構想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家的命運都掌握你的手裏了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.10,0:02:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你以為我能超過普萊西亞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.20,0:02:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很努力了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力了也超不過他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能我還是不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有；沒有；沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞當然是比普萊西亞差點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.30,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就想要寫出好劇本只會弄巧成拙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆點，放鬆點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我太激動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是我們也說了不該說的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不該說期待什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，先用放鬆的心情……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劇本已經寫完了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是興奮的睡不著了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了夜宵來看你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了，行了，再加把勁幹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是老闆想要什麼樣的劇目呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能只會說“不行！去改”之類的，真讓人搞不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.80,0:03:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得他只會說“去做”之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有表演《人魚公主》的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就應該告訴空讓她創造自己的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話，空那時就不用那麼煩惱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看呢？莎拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.80,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看？卡洛斯的性格一直是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.00,0:04:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團剛建立的時候就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.90,0:04:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個時候表演的內容\N都是自己一點一點的改進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.30,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天的劇目都會有新的改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使卡萊多劇團的名氣慢慢響起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.40,0:04:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天要做的事情幾乎是一成不變的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯的做事方式卻始終都沒有變呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.20,0:04:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果空的人魚公主\N是別人告訴你該怎麼做的會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還會覺得象現在這麼難忘嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.90,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，也有可能只是他覺得老自己想很麻煩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.20,0:04:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，決定了選擇什麼樣的故事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那個，要考慮人數的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.20,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想選用神鬼之類的愛情故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.60,0:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過劇情方面還需要更加別出心裁點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.90,0:04:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間屋子的資料裏或許能夠得到提示哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個劇目真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想試試啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道我會不會吹火把呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可是歌後啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要不要表演騎單車啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可還是要根據留下的人來安排表演內容啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的都覺得由利的劇團就那麼好麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.00,0:05:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有傳聞說，只要是卡萊多劇團\N辭職的都可以無條件的入團哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去試試嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的確是很有實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.20,0:05:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過可能不太好開口的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那如果有人引路就不同了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.30,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧，美亞，要超過莎士比亞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.10,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞也在努力，我也要努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.90,0:05:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團不是你想像中的那麼好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯欺騙了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好象睡不著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有心事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不用占卜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不會有好事的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來為你唱首歌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.60,0:06:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦嚕；啦嚕啦；睡不著；的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啦嚕啦；啦啦嚕；就這麼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽得我毛骨悚然，別嚕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.20,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞醒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一早就見過她一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在訓練室裏哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.90,0:06:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，剛聽說好象又有13個人退團了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，在哭嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撐著點，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼亂來很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說聲，我會教你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外，又有13個人退團了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼下去，只有10個人左右留下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽蒙•派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是繼續我們的話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.00,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，卡萊多劇團的情況我已經聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可即使如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯還是決定在\N下一場演出時起用外行人做導演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話，再這麼下去的話……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK，沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK？就這麼簡單？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我就一直對卡萊多劇團很有興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是卡洛斯他總是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會說服他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，只是覺得你很酷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認真點聽我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天後初稿會交上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果通過的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯就不可能再聽我們的意見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來，卡萊多劇團只會走向滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是苗木野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.40,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠來，我真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……就是上次說的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟卡萊多劇團是什麼樣我不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還是什麼都不明白怎麼能就來麻煩你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這裏我就覺得太兒戲了，所以……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一點都不擅長做戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是有話對我說吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.70,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.70,0:09:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要做出毀滅卡萊多劇團的事來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理由是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候知道的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概一年以前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由利•凱力亞是亞倫•布拉斯的兒子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱力亞好象是他母親的姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由利是在向我報復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我一直在等這個時機的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.10,0:09:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親和我一樣是位雜技藝術家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是卡萊多劇團的創始人之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.00,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我父親被卡洛斯殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那……那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.80,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來我這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.00,0:10:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裏還沒有頂級女星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.60,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完全具備這個資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.10,0:10:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果留下來的人大概也就十人左右了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由利那個傢伙真是不可饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧，美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太多地方難以決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.20,0:10:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果主人公的靈魂\N原來是雜技團的老闆怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成靈魂的主人公獨自\N回憶起了曾經熱鬧非凡的雜技團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.60,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來每個人的特長都可以充分發揮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.20,0:10:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他留下遺憾的只有他的原女友一位女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.40,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一幕是在美麗的回憶中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.50,0:11:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和最愛的人分別的動人場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個，一定行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這個劇本會很轟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我就超越了莎士比亞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然我的擔心不是多餘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞看來還是沒什麼經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是再演賽蒙•派克的劇目《灰姑娘》吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，卡洛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽蒙•派克要見您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請他進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你決定了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.30,0:12:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞，你可以下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的表演就由美亞•齊安姆擔任導演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去修改劇本，期限還有四天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.40,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，看來這次也沒有合作的機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.10,0:12:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次一起參加舞會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽蒙•派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.30,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想請你擔任特級助導，協助美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯，你這麼做太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，好象很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事，要先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劇本就發到我的電子郵件裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他還有什麼就等我修改之後再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回頭見咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個賽蒙•派克……協助我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.40,0:13:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，那個天才賽蒙•派克居然會看我的劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想到這個，我就覺得幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論要怎麼修改我都會交出完美的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.20,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我自己先再看一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞已經一步步的進入狀態了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能再老是這麼消沉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.60,0:13:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由利的事還是要向老闆好好的證實一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.00,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要出門？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？原來由利他是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯強迫我父親表演危險的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後利用我父親的死來製造影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.20,0:14:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的確有很多好事者對亞倫的死很感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.60,0:14:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謠言傳的沸沸揚揚的\N觀眾也增加了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過最後要表演的\N那個動作是亞倫自己的意願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說，由利他……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實由利他不可能不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是強迫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果本人害怕的話是不可能跳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.40,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這件事卡洛斯一直在責備自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直對由利的所作所為保持沈默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不容易解決的事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.20,0:14:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就不用擔這個心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要好好的考慮自己的表演內容就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，請稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽蒙•派克找美亞的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.80,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從第二頁到第四頁都刪了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後從第五頁的中間開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.70,0:15:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到第二十四頁都刪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.00,0:15:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後，結局要改……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個，這部分是主人公和戀人分別的場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，不過這類的結局太普遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刪掉的那些部分換些有意思的情節吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.50,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有高潮幕，製作二，三個精彩場面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.20,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說全部都要改了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是去向老闆請辭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我還是不夠資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要放棄了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.90,0:16:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，這樣下去如果還是不行\N的話只會給大家添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種不負責任的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得你行的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.00,0:16:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為卡洛斯是絕對不會\N讓不合適的人去做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要美亞寫的劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不希望你輸給普萊西亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.70,0:16:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己不行就放棄，那就什麼都完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習三重影絕技的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.60,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好多次的認為自己不夠格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實也是，沒有一次不掉下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那時你對我們說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想和阿娜，和空一起完成三重影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.80,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我暗想一定要成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定，一定要成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才那麼努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞，加油吧，直到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄，直到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.60,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄，不要放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.30,0:17:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不言放棄？不言放棄？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不言放棄的人們的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.20,0:17:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能能行，這不正和現在的我們相似嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.20,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然成員很少，不過卡萊多劇團還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個劇目成功的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開的人或許還會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.30,0:17:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個，如果表演具有這個意願的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，能行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就叫大家來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.50,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣，考慮到人數比較少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位在自己的上演節目中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.30,0:17:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人至少準備三種以上的表演節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有故事情節不能準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劇本還沒有完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完成？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劇本能夠完成嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠完成，絕對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.60,0:18:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家各自開始練習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.00,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，就是那樣捲曲身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.60,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，那麼這邊我就再改一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有意外的話，一切OK了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.80,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在創造自己的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好象又回到了那個時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢，再動下腦筋怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家來看下這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的跳竿怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.30,0:18:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的卡萊多劇團裏\N能夠做我的搭檔的只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你不願意，也一定要你來做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.90,0:19:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，真的很不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.10,0:19:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到期限為止還有八個小時，再加把勁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.90,0:19:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後的那幕再下點功夫\N讓觀眾的情緒沸騰起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.10,0:19:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呈現給觀眾的才是\N卡萊多劇團的招牌劇目哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，我盡力試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞，能行了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有句要說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.50,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的衣服要裙子短的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.70,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劇本相當完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.80,0:19:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周之後就是初演開幕日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻開始排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧，美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞臺是人類的黑暗世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的是那裏的不斷鬥爭\N的二個國家的年輕人的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.30,0:20:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個動作最好是更加粗野一點……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不過這樣也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自信點下指示吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.30,0:20:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們本來是很要好的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.10,0:20:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的夥伴們發生爭吵\N的同時危險卻在不斷加劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的排練每天都有新點子產生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.90,0:20:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些大型道具真讓我為難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬，你年輕了許多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜，再猛烈點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，動作幅度再大點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想劇目的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.40,0:20:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢想？希望？都是日語啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近開始學日語了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.80,0:20:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最危險的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.40,0:21:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主角間表現出來的是希望象\N從前一樣作為好夥伴共同生活的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.70,0:21:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久以後這種想法就傳遍了每個人的心底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.80,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放棄了互相的爭鬥，學會了寬容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家決心再次聚集所有人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.60,0:21:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了，我都能感受到舞臺高漲的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.70,0:21:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迎來解放的時候他們終於\N明白什麼才是自由的真正含義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.70,0:21:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以這個劇目的名字就叫“FREEDOM”（自由）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.70,0:21:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.20,0:21:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能成功，太開心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.80,0:22:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.00,0:22:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來的成員一定都會因為這喝彩聲而回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.10,0:22:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.80,0:22:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告：卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.40,0:22:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，向大家道歉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.60,0:22:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，美亞的劇目獲得了大大大成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.30,0:22:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為由利的陰謀……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是卡萊多劇團的最後一天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.30,0:22:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐，我們以後到底該！該！該！……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.30,0:22:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.20,0:22:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想，飛向空
